messages.content: Is it possible to speak to a head chef, or somebody who runs finance?

Hello There. Hope all is well. I am Kieran From GastroNorth / Direct / Food. We are market leaders in the design, supply and installation of professional food service systems in all sectors across the UK & Ireland. We have very competitive prices on all equipment, against our competitors. Would you like a quote for anything, I can quote you anything from crockery and cleaning supplies etc. to the heavier equipment like ovens, glasswashers etc.
